com.bigdata.bop.join

Interface IHashJoinUtilityFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface IHashJoinUtilityFactory
extends Serializable
    Interface for the factory pattern to create a IHashJoinUtility.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Olaf Hartig
    See Also:
    (by using such a factory as an annotation of {@link HashIndexOpBase} it becomes possible to get rid of the two earlier subclasses of {@link HashIndexOp} (namely, HTreeHashIndexOp and JVMHashIndexOp) which imposed the duplication of code)
